513
00:32:37,109 --> 00:32:38,027
Terima kasih.

514
00:32:39,905 --> 00:32:40,947
Saya…

515
00:32:44,285 --> 00:32:45,788
Bukankah awak agak kasar?

516
00:32:46,372 --> 00:32:47,831
Sebagai defendan?

