950
00:59:49,749 --> 00:59:50,960
Naib Dekan.

951
00:59:51,877 --> 00:59:55,006
Ini kelas pertama awak di sini.
Apa perasaan awak?

952
00:59:56,843 --> 00:59:58,427
Betul. Ya.

